<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV5">
<l>paṉippiyal vāka vuṭaiyataṇ vāṭaiyik kālamivvūr</l>
<l>paṉippiyal vellān tavirnteri vīcuman taṇṇantuḻāyp</l>
<l>paṉippuyal cōrun taṭaṅkaṇṇi māmaitti ṟattukkolām</l>
<l>paṉippuyal vaṇṇaṉceṅ kōloru nāṉṟu taṭāviyatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The cool north wind, that possesses [me] as [its] nature making me shiver,</l>
<l>stays this time in this village [and] hurls flames at all shivering natures. Has the just rule</l>
<l>of the one with the colour of dewy clouds, who is deadly for the dark [complexion]</l>
<l>of her with broad eyes that flow over with dewy rain for the pretty cool Tulsi, been bent [this] one time?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
